title: Great Barrier Reef corals facing fight for survival (The University of Queensland)
text: ( Source : The University of Queensland ) A global coral bleaching event expected to heavily impact the Great Barrier Reef has been confirmed by scientists from The University of Queensland and the National Ocean Atmospheric Administration . UQ
